dc_title_s: Lidar-Derived 18-in Bare Earth DEM (ft) for  Waushara County, WI 2024
dc_description_s: This data represents a Lidar-derived 18-in Bare Earth Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2024. This dataset has elevation values in feet and is in the WISCRS coordinate system for Waushara County: EPSG 7644. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features.
uw_supplemental_s: Detailed metadata for the tiles used to create this countywide file:https://web.s3.wisc.edu/wsco-wisconsinview/lidar/Waushara/Waushara_2024_3DEP_Delivery/Metadata/Metadata.zip.
